  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Des Dromonts is offered on a half board basis, breakfast and evening meals are included. Drinks are payable locally.</p>
<p>Each day enjoy a continental breakfast buffet with a choice of breads, pastries, fresh fruit, as well as meats and cheeses from the region,  additional hot options are also available.</p>
<p>Dinner is served in the Les Enfants Terribles bistro restaurant, each evening you can enjoy a three course evening meal with a choice of menu. If you would prefer a more laid back dining option, you can also dine in Le Festival serving a range of local specialties and burgers - guests are provided with a €55 credit which covers three courses, </p>
<p> </p>
<p>New Year Gala dinners available (additional supplement)</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
