  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic bedrooms</strong> are around 18m² and sleep two people. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy, please call our Reservations team to book.</p>
<p><strong>Club bedrooms</strong> are slightly larger than Classic bedrooms at around 22m² and sleep two people. These rooms can also accommodate a cot.</p>
<p><strong>Superior bedrooms</strong> are around 25m² and sleep two people, there is also a bath in the bedroom.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are around 36m² and sleep two adults and two children. The suites have a master bedroom separated from the lounge by a sliding door, and pull-out sofa bed which can accommodate two children under 12 years old in the lounge area. These rooms have a bathroom with a shower and bathtub, with a separate toilet. </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>South facing views</li>
<li>Bathroom with a shower </li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Mini bar</li>
<li>Nespresso machine</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Baby kits including cot, night light, bottle warmer, changing table and bath are available on request from the reception (reserve in advance €25 per day supplement)</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that the hotel is pet friendly</p>]]></roomsDescription>
